OL,3,C'I hope that this isn't the end of the
OL,4,Cstory' - actor speaks out on steelworks
OL,6,FFollowing seven months of discussions
OL,7,Fwith unions, Tata revealed last
OL,8,FThursday it is proceeding with its
OL,9,F#1.25 billion investment in an
OL,10,Felectric arc furnace on the Port
OL,11,FTalbot site and will close the two
OL,12,Fblast furnaces by the end of June and
OL,13,Fend of September respectively.
OL,15,FThe move is expected to see 2,800 jobs
OL,16,Flost, the majority at its site in Port
OL,17,FTalbot.
