OL,3,C'I hope that this isn't the end of the
OL,4,Cstory' - actor speaks out on steelworks
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales' Backstage
OL,7,Fprogramme, the actor said: "Ever since
OL,8,FI can remember the steelworks being
OL,9,Fthere, all my life it's always been
OL,10,Funder threat.
OL,12,F"So it's not like it came as a massive
OL,13,Fsurprise, although it's still a huge
OL,14,Fshock obviously."
OL,16,FSheen is currently starring in Nye - a
OL,17,Fnew play about the life of NHS founder
OL,18,FAneurin Bevan.
