OL,3,C'I hope that this isn't the end of the
OL,4,Cstory' - actor speaks out on steelworks
OL,6,F"The wind has been blowing in one
OL,7,Fdirection for a very long time," he
OL,8,Fcontinued.
OL,10,FHe added: "I hope that that's not the
OL,11,Fend of the story."
OL,13,FSheen shared his concern for the local
OL,14,Fcommunity, adding: "Not only is it
OL,15,Fgoing to affect people and families
OL,16,Fand the community financially and
OL,17,Feconomically, but also
OL,18,Fpsychologically. The steelworks is the
OL,19,Fheart of the town and so what that
OL,20,Fwill do to the psyche of the town as
OL,21,Fwell is hard to really underestimate.
