OL,3,C'I hope that this isn't the end of the
OL,4,Cstory' - actor speaks out on steelworks
OL,6,F"I hope there's support there, I hope
OL,7,Fthat this isn't the end of the story,
OL,8,Fthat there's still a road to go down,
OL,9,Fbut whatever happens, I hope that
OL,10,Feverybody gets the support that they
OL,11,Fdeserve."
OL,13,FWhile unions and politicians have
OL,14,Fcriticised the decision, Tata has said
OL,15,Fit is planning the biggest investment
OL,16,Fin the steel industry for decades,
OL,17,Fsafeguarding the industry and
OL,18,Fpreserving 5,000 jobs.
